headline: Heavy Transportation Equipment Stocks Q4 Teardown: Shyft (NASDAQ:SHYF) Vs The Rest
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Shyft (NASDAQ:SHYF) and the rest of the heavy transportation equipment stocks fared in Q4.
